      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="volunteering"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->Volunteering
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2026/03/Kaytana-2026-Ad.png" href="https://onebes.uk/kaytana" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2025/10/Drivers-for-Survivors.png?v3" href="mailto:nicola.strauther@holocaust.org.uk?subject=Drivers%20for%20Survivors" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/09/we-need-your-help-1.jpg" href="https://tinyurl.com/bes-security-signup" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/03/Willesden-Jewish-Cemetery-Flyer.png" href="https://willesdenjewishcemetery.org.uk" />
          <mj-text><strong>Would you like to give newcomers a warm welcome at BES?</strong> Join the new Buddies Network today and help us grow our community, meet new people and create a welcoming environment. Become a buddy, or find out more by contacting <a href="mailto:welcome@borehamwoodshul.org">welcome@borehamwoodshul.org</a></mj-text>
          <mj-image src="https://bes-website.s3.amazonaws.com/web-images/buddies-network.jpeg?mtime=20231015162340&focal=none" alt="Join the BES Buddies Network" href="mailto:welcome@borehamwoodshul.org" />
          <mj-image src="https://bes-website.s3.amazonaws.com/web-images/welcoming-team.jpeg?mtime=20231015162339&focal=none" alt="Welcoming Team" />
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="kids"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->Kids
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2026/01/kaytana26-kids.png?v2" href="https://onebes.uk/kaytana" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2025/11/Anim-Zemirot-Club-Yavneh.jpg" />
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="crp"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->CRP - Certificate of Religious Practice
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="15px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2026/03/05_CRP_2026.jpg" href="https://www.theus.org.uk/crp" />
          <mj-text>
            <p class="title"><strong>Collection of CRP points to start school in Sept 2027 has started.</strong></p>
            <p>You must register each child you plan to collect CRP points via synagogue attendance here: <a href="https://myus.theus.org.uk/crp-application/crp-user-login/">myus.theus.org.uk/crp-application/crp-user-login/</a></p>
            <p>The dates eligible for CRP collection are between <strong>18th April 2026</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>9th January 2027</strong>&nbsp;(but please check with the school you are applying to as deadlines differ), both BES@Croxdale &amp; BES@Yavneh will be using the United Synagogue system,&nbsp;<strong>if you plan to attend both sites, you will need to register separately for each</strong>.</p>
            <p><strong>CRP Desk</strong></p>
            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The CRP desk is where the sheets are handed out to those arriving to record CRP attendance. We rely on volunteers to run the desk, so please help if you can. If no one volunteers, there will be no CRP desk that day. <strong><a href="https://borehamwoodshul.org/crp-desk-sign-up">Please sign up here.</a></strong></span></p>
            <p>FAQ’s and more information on CRP can be found here: <a href="https://www.theus.org.uk/crp">www.theus.org.uk/crp</a> or contact <a href="mailto:crp@borehamwoodshul.org">crp@borehamwoodshul.org</a></p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="youth"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->Youth
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2025/11/Club-NXT.png" href="mailto:rabbigreg@borehamwoodshul.org" />
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="care"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->BES Care
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2026/03/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-23-at-12.51.25.jpeg" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2026/04/WhatsApp-Image-2026-04-21-at-14.28.39.jpeg" href="https://theus.org.uk/singingformemory" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/11/chatty-cafe-jcare.jpg" />
          <mj-image src="https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/4280d4e8-33ef-4d27-8d49-9d21325369b2/Synagogue-2/editor_images/Hardship%202.png" alt="BES Hardship Fund" href="https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/borehamwood-hardship-fund" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/02/BESCare-Here-to-help.png" />
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-divider />
          <mj-text padding-top="0" padding-bottom="0">
            <p class="title">Community Dementia Programmes</p>
            <p>Through different services, JCare help people living with dementia and their family carers to live well and access the support they need.</p>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button href="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/02/Community-Dementia-Programmes-POSTER.pdf">Download Community Dementia Programmes</mj-button>
          <mj-text>
            <p>If you or someone you know may benefit from some support, please contact, in confidence, Karen <a href="tel:07341005116">07341 005 116</a> / <a href="mailto:care@borehamwoodshul.org">care@borehamwoodshul.org</a></p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
